, 121 figs. 1, 2—habit and calyx—as 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Buxbaum" authorityYear="1924" box="[407,652,1274,1301]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Droseraceae" genus="Drosera" kingdom="Plantae" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="47" pageNumber="48" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="variety" species="villosa" variety="bifurca">
<emphasis box="[407,517,1274,1300]" italics="true" pageId="47" pageNumber="48">D. villosa</emphasis>
