<bibRefCitation author="Gonella, P. M. &amp; Rivadavia, F. &amp; Sano, P. T. &amp; Fleischmann, A." box="[675,944,1274,1300]" pageId="47" pageNumber="48" pagination="1 - 40" refId="ref56124" refString="Gonella, P. M., Rivadavia, F., Sano, P. T. &amp; Fleischmann, A. (2014) Exhuming Saint-Hilaire: revision of the Drosera villosa complex (Droseraceae) supports 200 year-old neglected species concepts. Phytotaxa 156 (1): 1 - 40. http: // dx. doi. org / 10.11646 / phytotaxa. 156.1.1" type="journal article" year="2014">
